      <title>政策支持下1月新增银行贷款创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-january-new-bank-loans-hit-record-high-policy-support-2024-02-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着央行采取行动提振陷入困境的经济，中国 1 月份新增银行贷款增幅超出预期，创历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-january-new-bank-loans-hit-record-high-policy-support-2024-02-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 08:05:36 GMT</pubDate>
